title: With Byrd at the South Pole [1930 - USA] adventure documentary
description: With Byrd at the South Pole [1930 - USA] Documentary / Adventure http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0020594/ Drama of human daring and courage at the bottom of the world! Floyd Gibbons narrates a filmed record of Rear Admiral Richard E. Byrd's journey by sea from New York to Antarctica and his flight over the continent. This was the first documentary film to win an Academy Award and the only documentary film ever to win Best Cinematography.
